snippet.title: MALIKI : POISON OF THE PAST [GAMES] Annoucement Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-Order the game now : https://www.kunekune.fr/malikipop

Add to your wishlist : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2893260/Maliki__Poison_Of_The_Past

Join Maliki and her wacky family in their epic battle against Poison, a fearsome plant creature that has colonized space-time.  Go along on a fantastic odyssey through the ages that provides a unique mix of exploration, temporal riddles and turn-based fights full of surprises.
